        This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Dignicom Inc. ("Dignicom", "we") collects, uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users ("User", "you") of the English Cosmos website ("Website") hosted at www.englc.com. This privacy policy applies to all products and services offered by Dignicom on the Website.<br>
